runway ( malayalam : റൺവേ ) is a 2004 malayalam crime film written by udayakrishna and siby k. thomas and directed by joshiy .   it stars dileep , indrajith , murali , kavya madhavan and harisree ashokan .   the film revolves around the unni ( dileep ) who due to financial problems becomes the renowned smuggler valayar paramasivam in the kerala-tamil nadu border check post walayar .   the film was a box office blockbuster .   in this movie dileep plays the role of a gangster , who works for a mafia king pin .   murali plays the role of the kingpin , who fights against chinnadankalasala babu .